Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World,\N the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally\N entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled\N by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They landed on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an island with two parts,\N one burning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After learning about the ruler of \Nthe island - Caesar Clown's motive,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all while trying to escape Shinokuni,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with their pirate ally -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Warlord - Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they are on the move to kidnap Caesar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,save the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and escape from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After falling into a garbage dump,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy met a dragon named Momonosuke -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who has the same name as the boy that \Nthe samurai Kin'emon was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're... flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Pirate Hunter Zoro
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a 120 million berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a Logia-type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Deadly Fight in a Blizzard! \NThe Straw Hats vs. the Snow Woman!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:02.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,600)}B BUILDING 3RD FLOOR - THE BISCUIT ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must stop the children quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are gonna\N leave the room soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised her that I will hold them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I put Mocha in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper-chan told me\N what these candies do to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mocha! Give us the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't eat these candies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to your senses, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha, we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said we couldn't\N see our parents now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If adults get infected with the \Ndisease we have, they'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want your mother\N and father die, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get good treatment\N for a year and get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Caesar Clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Master."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are a part of my \Nfirst-generation of patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward\N to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you were scared and worried
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you heard\N that you're sick out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everything is okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will treat you at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my only son to this disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never wanna see another\N child suffering from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I don't wanna see another parent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lose their child and have to grieve like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing.\N I shouldn't cry in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Master-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. You're very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes! I must introduce you to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're from other islands \Nbut have the same disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Uzu. Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Doran.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Konbu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have some new friends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach them about this place, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody! Be nice to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if you need any help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Monet-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monet-san was kind\N but she was lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a reward for\N enduring with the treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a candy from the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's escape from here together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to your senses now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta catch up with the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he coming this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Nami! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use me as a shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying\N to attack the weak ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strategic to finish off\N easier foes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, move out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat Egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat worked, just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat Burglar -
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a 16 million berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hid herself in the snow again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wanna fight me,\N snow woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow Fence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perpetual Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snow is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold! I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cuatro Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spank!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those children are the Master's \Nprecious test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm responsible for protecting \NCaesar and his experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who planted this rebellious\N spirit in Mocha's mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids asked for help on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha, please hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are so uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single day, we treat them nicely
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and allow them to live in great comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you people are trying to do is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take away these "treasures" \Nfrom us "foster parents."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are like pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have no problem with it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop interfering with my duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skin Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! We can get out of here like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!\N What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hungry at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Monet doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The children are getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can always restock\N guinea pigs through kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our priority now is providing \Na showcase for Shinokuni
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and getting rid of the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the gas is\N flowing into the building,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the situation is favorable for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B Building will be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,filled up with gas soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no choice \Nbut to head to R Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna be killed\N by the gas anyway though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Oh no! Oh no! Oh no! Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Oh no! Oh no! Oh no! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did the gas flow in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the door was closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it leaking from somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, this building is no longer safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up to look for the \NSea Prism Stone Handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, you go with Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave him alone -\N he's too clumsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corpse-dono, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you at R Building!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been only defending yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without even trying to attack. Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I didn't think\N I could beat you but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...maybe I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find the children and\N take them out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't it a little cold here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go through the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's trying to take \Nthe children away from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you leading them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! I don't see any children
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's Pirate Hunter Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick out your lower lip\N and make fun of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they all slip on the snow, \Nhit their heads and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nami and Robin went ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go away already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What good information\N even from a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a cutie behind him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are so obnoxious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. But look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bird with a human face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a harpy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:19:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she's still cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather bewitchingly beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're enjoying this, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why is it snowing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting stormy\N all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened to my shoulder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's a Logia-type!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A swordsman using Haki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.47,0:22:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sealed off the door to the room \Nto prevent the gas from flowing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where it might start leaking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, do all you can\N to save the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:22:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you need my help here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monet attacks, using the powerful \NSnow-Snow Fruit powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Tashigi desperately fights \Nback by using her Haki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she is then caught by\N Monet's monstrous fangs,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and just as her shoulder is \Nabout to be torn to shreds,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro's beast-like instincts cause him into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.06,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Showing Off His Techniques!\N Zoro's Formidable One-Sword Style!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.78,0:23:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
